cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Citation Reliability in LLM-Assisted Academic Writing"
message: >-
  If you use this software or the empirical results in your
  own work, please cite the associated manuscript and this
  repository.
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: "Max (Mengxuan)"
    given-names: "Mengxuan"
    family-names: "Max"
repository-code: "https://github.com/mengx/citation-reliability-paper"
abstract: >-
  An empirical study evaluating citation reliability in LLM-assisted
  academic writing across four workflows, two languages, and two models.
  Includes prompts, verification data, manuscript artifacts, and a
  reusable verification pipeline.
keywords:
  - "large language models"
  - "citation hallucination"
  - "academic writing"
license: "CC-BY-4.0"
